---
import Container from "@components/Container.astro";
import PageLayout from "@layouts/PageLayout.astro";
import Link from "@components/Link.astro";
---

<PageLayout title="Collection" description="The 2667 Collection - NFTs by Shane Sarin">
  <Container>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-black dark:text-white">
          The 2667 Collection - Select Works
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
          2667 is more than a number—it's the edition of the Bored Ape that became one of the defining pieces in my journey as a collector. I started collecting NFTs to connect with groundbreaking digital artists and be part of a cultural shift in how we create, share, and value art. My collection reflects that journey—featuring work from visionaries like Pak and Beeple alongside a growing list of other creators I believe in. For me, it's never been about flipping or chasing the next big drop; it's about building a collection that tells a story and supports the artists shaping the future of digital creativity.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- The Fungible Collection -->
      <section class="space-y-6 pt-12">
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">The Fungible Collection</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">by Pak</p>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">A groundbreaking collection that redefined our understanding of value in digital art. Released via Sotheby's in April 2021, The Fungible challenged collectors to consider what makes something valuable.</p>
          <Link href="https://www.sothebys.com/en/digital-catalogues/the-fungible-collection-by-pak" external>Learn more →</Link>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-6">
          <div class="group">
            <div class="aspect-square overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-black">
              <video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
                <source src="/collection/ACube.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
              </video>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">A Cube</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">Pak</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-500">#481/5148</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group">
            <div class="aspect-square overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-black">
              <video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
                <source src="/collection/FiveCubes.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
              </video>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">Five Cubes</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">Pak</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-500">#424/571</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group">
            <div class="aspect-square overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-black">
              <video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
                <source src="/collection/Ten_Cubes.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
              </video>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">Ten Cubes</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">Pak</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-500">#100/247</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group">
            <div class="aspect-square overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-black">
              <video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
                <source src="/collection/Twenty_Cubes.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
              </video>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">Twenty Cubes</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">Pak</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-500">#20/120</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group">
            <div class="aspect-square overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-black">
              <video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
                <source src="/collection/Complexity.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
              </video>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">Complexity</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">Pak</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-500">#59/100</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 pt-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">* Fun fact: I placed second in Pak's contest to predict the total sales for The Fungible drop. The final total was $16.8M—I guessed $16.69M. <span class="not-italic">😎</span></p>
          <div class="max-w-md mt-6">
            <blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-dnt="true">
              <p lang="en" dir="ltr">The Oracle results for The Fungible.<br><br>1st: dylanh (<a href="https://twitter.com/0xdylanh">@0xdylanh</a>) — $16,815,999 (off by $10,000)<br>2nd: shanesarin — $16,690,000<br>3rd: jonty (<a href="https://twitter.com/jonty">@jonty</a>) — $16,888,888<br><br>DM me with your ETH address to claim your prize. 🎉</p>&mdash; Pak (@muratpak) <a href="https://twitter.com/muratpak/status/1383165981258874885">April 16, 2021</a>
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- The Title Collection -->
      <section class="space-y-6 pt-12">
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">The Title</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">by Pak</p>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">Released in December 2020, The Title is a conceptual NFT collection built around a single repeated image sold at different prices, with only the token's name changing. Each NFT shares the same artwork, but variations in title and scarcity highlight how value in crypto art often stems more from ownership, labeling, and perceived rarity than from visual difference. One work in the series, pointedly named "The Unsold," carried a $1,000,000 list price, sharpening the project's critique of speculation and value in the NFT space.</p>
          <Link href="https://www.niftygateway.com/collections/thetitle/" external>Learn more →</Link>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-6">
          <div class="group">
            <div class="aspect-square overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-black">
              <video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
                <source src="/collection/TheFlipper.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
              </video>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">The Flipper</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">Pak</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-500">#66/99</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">Notice anything interesting about the edition number?</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Ash Chapter One: Carbon -->
      <section class="space-y-6 pt-12">
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">Ash Chapter One: Carbon</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">by Pak</p>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">Released in January 2022 as the first drop in Pak's ASH project, Ash Chapter One: Carbon includes one unique 1-of-1 NFT and 999 editioned NFTs. It uses a burn system where users burn ASH tokens to create, upgrade, or delete the artworks. This setup makes NFTs part of a changing system of value, where burned items leave behind ash that acts as both money and a symbol of how value changes in digital art.</p>
          <Link href="https://burn.art/drops/carbon" external>Learn more →</Link>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-6">
          <div class="group">
            <div class="aspect-square overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-black">
              <video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
                <source src="/collection/Carbon.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
              </video>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">Carbon</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">Pak</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-500">#434/999</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group">
            <div class="aspect-square overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-black">
              <video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
                <source src="/collection/TheGoldVanguard.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
              </video>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">The Gold Vanguard</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">Pak</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-500">#763/999</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group">
            <div class="aspect-square overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-black">
              <video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
                <source src="/collection/CheapCarbon.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
              </video>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">Cheap Carbon</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">Pak</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-500">#515/999</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Ash Chapter Two: Metamorphosis -->
      <section class="space-y-6 pt-12">
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">Ash Chapter Two: Metamorphosis</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">by Pak (featuring 30 artists)</p>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">Released in March 2022 as the second drop in Pak's ASH project, Ash Chapter Two: Metamorphosis offers an edition of 7500 tokens quoting Kafka's tale of Gregor Samsa's transformation into a vermin. Each wallet can mint up to 10 tokens revealing art from 30 creators like Pak, Paris Hilton, and Mad Dog Jones (250 per creator), with mechanics to combine any 5 tokens to morph one—destroying 4 to reduce supply and enable high-tier burns. This setup turns initial artworks into evolving forms, probing how scarcity, destruction, and adaptation redefine value in digital art.</p>
          <Link href="https://burn.art/drops/metamorphosis" external>Learn more →</Link>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-6">
          <div class="group">
            <div class="aspect-square overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-black">
              <video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
                <source src="/collection/ThatRoom.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
              </video>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">That Room</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">Pak</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-500">#97/250</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group">
            <div class="aspect-square overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-black">
              <video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
                <source src="/collection/MonstrousVermin.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
              </video>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">Monstrous Vermin</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">Pak</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-500">#213/250</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group">
            <div class="aspect-square overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-black">
              <video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
                <source src="/collection/SunlightOveraCity.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
              </video>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">Sunlight Over a City, 2022</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">LIŔONA</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-500">#240/250</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group">
            <div class="aspect-square overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-black">
              <video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
                <source src="/collection/IridescentImagination.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
              </video>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">Iridescent Imagination</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">Mad Dog Jones</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-500">#243/250</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- The 2020 Collection: Beeple Everydays -->
      <section class="space-y-6 pt-12">
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">The 2020 Collection: Beeple Everydays</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">by Beeple</p>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">Released on NiftyGateway in December 2020, The 2020 Collection assembles 722 unique NFTs from Beeple's daily "Everydays" series, transforming one-a-day surreal visions into a cyberpunk NFT archive. Works span editions like "BULL RUN" (271 pieces), "INTO THE ETHER" (207 pieces), "INFECTED" (123 pieces), and "Beeple Everydays - Raw" (100 pieces).</p>
          <Link href="https://beeple-collect.com/collection-all/2020-collection/" external>Learn more →</Link>
        </div>
        
        <div class="max-w-md mt-6">
          <div class="group">
            <div class="aspect-auto overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-black">
              <video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
                <source src="/collection/Bullrun.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
              </video>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">BULL RUN</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">Beeple</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-500">#14/271</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>


      <!-- EVERYDAY ARTIFACTS -->
      <section class="space-y-6 pt-12">
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">EVERYDAY ARTIFACTS</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">by Beeple</p>
          <p class="text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">During the grand opening of BEEPLE STUDIOS on March 11, 2023, Beeple unleashed a dramatic cascade of papers from the ceiling, concealing among them 100 special physical artifacts—each etched with a unique yellow barcode redeemable for exclusive NFTs drawn from his iconic daily "Everydays" series. I was lucky enough to catch edition #14/100 and even got Beeple to sign the physical version.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-2xl mt-6">
          <div class="group">
            <div class="aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-black">
              <img src="/collection/everydayartifact.png" alt="Everyday Artifact NFT" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" />
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">EVERYDAY ARTIFACT</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">Beeple</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-500">#14/100</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group">
            <div class="aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-black">
              <img src="/collection/everydayartifact-signed.jpg" alt="Signed Physical Artifact" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" />
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">Signed Physical</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">Beeple</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 italic">"Extravaluable Green Dot!" — Beeple</p>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>
  </Container>
</PageLayout>

<script is:inline async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js"></script>
